column1: - `oldb:administrator_level`: The government division that controls functions of the public land. List type. Examples:
- `admin0`: Top-level land holding by a continent
- `special`: Land holdings by a special district or division.
- `oldb:administrator_name`: Name of the managing land agency. List type.
- `oldb:designation`: What the administrator calls this type of public land. List type.
